Blocks.Text: As a friendly reminder, merchants that accepted Visa and Mastercard from January 1, 2004 through January 25, 2019 remain eligible to participate in a $5.5
billion settlement. The current deadline for claim submission is May 31, 2024. To learn more or submit your claim, please go to:
https://www.paymentcardsettlement.com. Nothing in this message is intended to provide legal advice.
